column2: Think of a superpower. For example, going anywhere instantly, travelling in time, reading minds.
Ask your teen “If you had the superpower to […] how would you use it?”
Encourage them to give themselves a superhero name and act like a superhero.
Now let them choose a super power for you.
Make sure you act it out too!",,,,,,,,,,,,,,,14f60b89-834f-43c1-9af0-e30943ff10d0,,execute_actions,;
